<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로그인 완료</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>로그인 완료</h1>
    <p>환영합니다, <%= userInfo.name || userInfo.preferred_username || userInfo.email %>님!</p> 
    <a href="/logout" class="button">로그아웃</a> <!-- 로그아웃 버튼 -->
</body>
</html>